name: coracoid process
definition: the protruding finger off the lateral border of the scapula that helps to hold the arm in the socket

name: costal cartilage
definition: dense cartilage that joins the ribcage to the sternum

name: crackius maximus
definition: the crack at the base of the sacrum between the two gluteus maximus muscles

name: biceps brachii
definition: two-headed muscle that lies on the upper arm between the shoulder and the elbow
